{"tid":829002,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"NBA的空中飛人🏀🏀🌟🌟🏆🏆","createTime":"2018-09-20T05:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T12:20:48.000Z","uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0c88657a74fb89642fde09f3a41e475be7fa1abf","tid":829002,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T05:45:33.000Z","msg":"NBA 第一個由罰球線跳上去入樽的空中飛人是J博士 <span style=\"color: red;\">Julius Erving</span>, 他在1976入樽賽裡表演過。<br />\n<br />\n然後到<span style=\"color: red;\">Michael Jordan</span> 在1985、1987和1988入樽賽裡表演過, 他曾經說過J博士是他的榜樣。<br />\n<br />\n接著到<span style=\"color: red;\">Brent Barry</span>，1996年入樽賽用單手飛上入樽。<br />\n<br />\n然後到2000年<span style=\"color: red;\">Vince Carter</span> 在入樽賽內雙手罰球線跳上入樽，雖然跳的時候明顯過了罰球線，但他也曾經在NBA真正比賽內偷球後單手在罰球線飛上入樽，被稱為「加拿大空中飛人」。<br />\n<br />\n然後到最瘋狂的<span style=\"color: red;\">Zach LaVine</span> 參加了2015 &amp; 2016 入樽賽：他在罰球線跳上，在空中的時候做大風車入樽，然後再降落地上。亦有罰球線飛上Alley-oop 入樽，真是一山還有一山高:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ifHc9fTXvTo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DifHc9fTXvTo&d=kThX8bkn0l1ex4g4vi8cw0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=14dd8a74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ifHc9fTXvTo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Giannis Antetokounmpo</span>也曾經在2017真正比賽上做過此入樽動作：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=18&amp;v=9ja8r2SStJs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D18%26v%3D9ja8r2SStJs&d=kThX8bkn0l1ex4g4vi8cw0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=57702eb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=18&amp;v=9ja8r2SStJs</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">誰是你們最喜歡的NBA空中飛人？</span>"},{"pid":"18d49c59f4ab3692f4ac62454913c3a8dda16476","tid":829002,"uid":54025,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nba.com/media/hawks/SmithDunk_1280x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nba.com%2Fmedia%2Fhawks%2FSmithDunk_1280x1024.jpg&h=d9f03578&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a456cfbf788ef3faadf7d81f7b0d6b0f8a71894","tid":829002,"uid":197098,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:56:39.000Z","msg":"雲斯卡達"},{"pid":"9b217b7dc10df430d1a46234c5cc0b5110497441","tid":829002,"uid":75533,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:01:03.000Z","msg":"輕鬆王"},{"pid":"9dff9df336ca7ab14fa84dc8e9d89989a19e6756","tid":829002,"uid":194908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"Nate Robinson"},{"pid":"cf01f6a48a3a6ac0b974406617166a3d94d1b12d","tid":829002,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:20:22.000Z","msg":"c朗"},{"pid":"c8df27f0efa2499c5525779a74203c1e4f80d154","tid":829002,"uid":144472,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:23:18.000Z","msg":"Shannon Brown<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/172316_c5acba4de638a769d055bf4ab1b47deb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F172316_c5acba4de638a769d055bf4ab1b47deb.jpg&h=5761adb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/20/172316_c0bcba466120fd695c4f3f95706da19c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F172316_c0bcba466120fd695c4f3f95706da19c.jpg&h=09959962&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"581baad3876a631c16dd51682667569a63b6eb74","tid":829002,"uid":175032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:28:49.000Z","msg":"鐘意睇矮撚<br />\n騰空耐更加有飛既感覺<br />\nSteve Francis"},{"pid":"f3f0cb785512c42612b1209371c3debebaaa7556","tid":829002,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T11:02:53.000Z","msg":"米高佐敦"